<P class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt?>OK time to continue the Summit Summary <img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-wink.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0>&nbsp; Sorry this is getting posted so late.</P>
<P class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt?><namespace prefix = o ns = "http://www.lithium.com/unique/URI">&nbsp;</P>
<P class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt?>So after the second session we had lunch.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>The discussions from the prior 2 sessions continued at lunch.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>Rashere sat with the Wizards to discuss the specifics for the manaburn changes.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>The EQLive team is again scattered through out the room...</P>
<P class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt?>&nbsp;</P>
<P class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt?>Here are some lunch photos; I was walking around blinding everyone.<FONT face="Times New Roman"><FONT color=#000000><FONT size=3></FONT></FONT></FONT></P></DIV>
<DIV><IMG src="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/images/forum_images/community/LVFanFaire2005/Summit_Lunch_2.jpg"></DIV>
<DIV><EM><FONT size=1>From left to right - Majax our Enchanter Correspondent, Grunts our Ranger Correspondent, and the back of Tastian's head our Beastlord correspondent (He is a bit camera shy)</FONT></EM></DIV>
